message: “We are passionate about raising the necessary awareness to put a stop to these horrific crimes. Our community cannot continue to be affected by this devastating trade,” said FNU President/CEO Dr. Maria C. Regueiro. “Join us at our collaborative walk, so together, we can save our youth!”

data.description: In recognition of National Human Trafficking Awareness Month in January, Florida National University, its POWERHOUSE Steering Committee, and the Dr. Jose Regueiro Foundation will host the Third Ann…
data.title: Florida National University hosts Human Trafficking Awareness Walk
